@NODE Req "Requirements"
@{B}Requirements@{UB}
You will need the following things to run the program:

- MUI
- An Internet connection
- NList.mcc 0.89

TView allocates 16384 (16k) bytes of stack. StackSnoop says it uses <7k so...
Me myself always has 50k stack anyway, so if you run into problems,
try increasing the stack ...

@ENDNODE

