@NODE Bugs "Bugs"
@{B}Documented Features@{UB}
o The cycle gadget won't change on a Load data, so make sure it's the same.
  Channels loaded, and channels configured, that is.
o Arexx-scripts relies on rx being in sys:rexxc drawer.
o Alarmtime says "5 min" but its what time you have configured.
o Locale-files are old.

If you find any bugs you can report them to me.
If you get an enforcer/cyberguard hit, please send me a copy of the output.

Email: rutgers@mhd.mh.se

@ENDNODE

